public class BulkCampaignLocationAdExtension
extends BulkAdExtensionAssociation

Represents a campaign level call ad extension. This class exposes properties that can be read and written as fields of the Campaign Location Ad Extension record in a bulk file. For more information, see Campaign Location Ad Extension at http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=511534.

See Also:
BulkServiceManager, BulkOperation, BulkFileReader, BulkFileWriter
